♫ I release my thoughts of you to be blown away into the air ♫

00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:40.720
♫ Floating with my clean heart, letting them go far away ♫

00:00:40.720 --> 00:00:47.560
♫ The scent of potpuri blows with love from the heart ♫

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:55.560
♫ I only hope that they reach you, the person who’s waiting ♫

00:00:55.560 --> 00:01:02.520
♫ Sending my thoughts of you to be blown away into the air ♫

00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:11.240
♫ Missing you is killing me, you might not understand ♫

00:01:11.240 --> 00:01:18.039
♫ I just want you to know, I don’t need anything else ♫

00:01:18.039 --> 00:01:27.320
♫ You don’t need to reluctantly accept if you don’t want to ♫

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:53.520
♫ I entrust this song to float and play through the air, ♫

00:01:53.520 --> 00:02:01.040
♫ floating by to you ♫

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:09.039
♫ Though it’s been a long time, I still love you ♫

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:15.240
♫ for as long as possible, for an infinite amount of time ♫

